titles.title: To correct the engrossment of the amendment of the House of Representatives to the Senate bill (S. 725).

action.text: Mr. Waxman asked unanimous consent to consider as introduced.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 9/20/1994--Introduced. Requests the Senate to return the House of Representatives amendment to S. 725 (traumatic brain injury research) to the House. Requires the Clerk of the House to make a specified change in the engrossment of the amendment.
